Dialogue: 0.0:17:39.05.0:17:40.02.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(79.408)}(WHISPERS) Where is he?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:40.42.0:17:44.09.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(142.408)}(POP MUSIC PLAYING ON RADIO)
Dialogue: 0.0:17:44.73.0:17:45.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(345.408)}You stay down there.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:49.43.0:17:50.69.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(61.408)}(KEYS JINGLING)
Dialogue: 0.0:17:53.07.0:17:54.04.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(133.405)}Be cool.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:57.41.0:17:59.57.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(177.408)}(MUSIC CONTINUES ON RADIO)
Dialogue: 0.0:18:13.42.0:18:14.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(259.405)}Turn around.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:15.56.0:18:16.52.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(303.408)}That way.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:24.27.0:18:25.23.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(354.405)}Donuts?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:26.17.0:18:27.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(131.408)}I thought it was tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:29.77.0:18:30.74.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(556.408)}(SIGHS)
Dialogue: 0.0:18:36.88.0:18:37.85.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(482.408)}Really?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:39.85.0:18:41.41.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(227.369)}DAVE: What the hell
Dialogue: 0.0:18:39.85.0:18:41.41.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(227.408)}is going on?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:42.62.0:18:43.71.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(179.408)}Just trying to make a living.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:44.65.0:18:46.21.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(389.372)}Armed robbery
Dialogue: 0.0:18:44.65.0:18:46.21.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(390.405)}is five to 10.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:46.45.0:18:47.42.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(134.408)}For squirt guns?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:48.42.0:18:49.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(120.408)}Doesn't matter. actually.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:50.19.0:18:51.45.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(93.372)}It does when you
Dialogue: 0.0:18:50.19.0:18:51.45.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(92.408)}pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:53.16.0:18:54.13.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(236.369)}You think
Dialogue: 0.0:18:53.16.0:18:54.13.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(236.408)}this is funny?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:54.43.0:18:55.76.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(121.369)}At least here
Dialogue: 0.0:18:54.43.0:18:55.76.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(120.408)}we get three square meals.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:56.20.0:18:57.26.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(113.405)}And a roof over our head.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:57.40.0:18:58.37.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(150.408)}Cute jumpers.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:58.47.0:18:59.43.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(124.408)}Oh. I love orange.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:59.53.0:19:00.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(240.408)}They do blue here.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:00.67.0:19:01.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(95.407)}Oh. even better.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:02.14.0:19:03.10.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(600.405)}Fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:03.74.0:19:04.71.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(354.405)}You could all rot.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:05.34.0:19:06.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(385.372)}We'll round up
Dialogue: 0.0:19:05.34.0:19:06.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(385.408)}your husband too.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:07.17.0:19:08.61.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(185.369)}But how will we
Dialogue: 0.0:19:07.17.0:19:08.61.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(183.408)}finish the job?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:09.24.0:19:11.11.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(264.372)}You didn't really give us
Dialogue: 0.0:19:09.24.0:19:11.11.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(265.408)}anything anyway.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:12.15.0:19:14.24.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(163.336)}Can you just ask
Dialogue: 0.0:19:12.15.0:19:14.24.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(162.372)}the security guard
Dialogue: 0.0:19:12.15.0:19:14.24.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(162.408)}for my phone?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:16.85.0:19:18.65.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(129.372)}I hate when people
Dialogue: 0.0:19:16.85.0:19:18.65.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(127.408)}don't respond to an e-vite.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:19.69.0:19:21.16.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(114.372)}Did gang friend
Dialogue: 0.0:19:19.69.0:19:21.16.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(113.408)}actually send a e-vite?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:23.32.0:19:24.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(343.408)}Paperless post.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:27.43.0:19:28.40.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(79.408)}When's the meeting?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:28.80.0:19:29.76.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(123.405)}Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:32.30.0:19:33.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(113.335)}You know.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:32.30.0:19:33.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(116.372)}I think it actually
Dialogue: 0.0:19:32.30.0:19:33.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(115.405)}kind of does
Dialogue: 0.0:19:33.63.0:19:34.73.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(97.372)}'cause if they
Dialogue: 0.0:19:33.63.0:19:34.73.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(98.407)}bail us out.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:34.84.0:19:36.46.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(122.369)}which it feels like
Dialogue: 0.0:19:34.84.0:19:36.46.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(122.408)}they're leaning towards.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:36.57.0:19:38.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(89.333)}then we could hit
Dialogue: 0.0:19:36.57.0:19:38.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(89.369)}that credit union
Dialogue: 0.0:19:36.57.0:19:38.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(91.405)}before it closes.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:38.67.0:19:40.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(358.372)}Uh. It's right
Dialogue: 0.0:19:38.67.0:19:40.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(358.405)}next to Walmart.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:41.21.0:19:42.18.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(76.405)}Twofer.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:42.71.0:19:44.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(123.372)}Might want to hang tight
Dialogue: 0.0:19:42.71.0:19:44.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(122.408)}in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:44.58.0:19:46.48.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(115.372)}We'll probably be back here
Dialogue: 0.0:19:44.58.0:19:46.48.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(117.408)}before that meeting.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:48.75.0:19:50.22.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(239.372)}We'll put you
Dialogue: 0.0:19:48.75.0:19:50.22.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(240.408)}on payroll.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:50.52.0:19:51.51.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(94.405)}Same amount as our cut.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:52.62.0:19:53.59.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(447.408)}Not happening.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:53.82.0:19:54.79.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(432.405)}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:55.39.0:19:57.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(208.405)}Never knocked over a casino.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:58.33.0:19:59.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(145.408)}Open all night.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:59.39.0:20:00.42.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(83.405)}Loaded with cash.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:00.53.0:20:01.50.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(125.408)}And on every corner.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:01.60.0:20:03.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(111.305)}How did we not
Dialogue: 0.0:20:01.60.0:20:03.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(109.341)}think of this before?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:01.60.0:20:03.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(388.408)}I just did.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:03.40.0:20:04.37.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(54.408)}(LAUGHS)
Dialogue: 0.0:20:11.91.0:20:12.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(54.408)}(DOOR OPENS)
Dialogue: 0.0:20:14.88.0:20:15.84.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(150.408)}(SIGHS)
Dialogue: 0.0:20:17.41.0:20:18.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(331.405)}Come here.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:24.29.0:20:25.25.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(97.408)}Your guy came through?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:26.65.0:20:27.62.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(449.405)}You tell me.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:28.39.0:20:29.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(204.405)}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:32.59.0:20:33.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(422.405)}Real or fake?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:35.26.0:20:37.25.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(119.308)}As long as
Dialogue: 0.0:20:35.26.0:20:37.25.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(120.344)}it pays the bills.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:35.26.0:20:37.25.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(406.405)}Come on.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:38.53.0:20:40.23.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(50.408)}(BREATHES DEEPLY)
Dialogue: 0.0:20:40.33.0:20:41.30.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(153.405)}Real.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:44.54.0:20:45.51.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(187.405)}Fake?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:49.94.0:20:50.91.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(150.369)}I can't tell
Dialogue: 0.0:20:49.94.0:20:50.91.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(147.405)}the difference.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:51.71.0:20:52.68.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(398.408)}That's the point.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:56.78.0:20:57.95.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(121.372)}What's that got
Dialogue: 0.0:20:56.78.0:20:57.95.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(121.405)}to do with it?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:58.85.0:20:59.84.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(255.405)}You want a cut or not?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:00.39.0:21:01.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(184.405)}You know it.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:01.52.0:21:03.96.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(168.372)}Then we gotta show your guy
Dialogue: 0.0:21:01.52.0:21:03.96.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(170.408)}how valuable you are.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:06.83.0:21:08.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(303.372)}It's missing
Dialogue: 0.0:21:06.83.0:21:08.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(300.408)}the engraved logo.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:10.40.0:21:11.37.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(436.408)}Right here.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:12.40.0:21:13.37.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(360.405)}In the corner.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:13.90.0:21:16.93.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(190.372)}Can't sleep on the stitching.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:13.90.0:21:16.93.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(190.408)}At least 10 stitches per inch.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:17.57.0:21:19.01.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(218.372)}Got to be symmetrical
Dialogue: 0.0:21:17.57.0:21:19.01.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(218.405)}on all sides.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:20.94.0:21:21.91.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(220.405)}The real ones...
Dialogue: 0.0:21:24.45.0:21:25.54.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(320.408)}come with a dust bag.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:26.91.0:21:27.88.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(78.405)}What's that?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:28.32.0:21:29.41.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(442.372)}It's like a bag
Dialogue: 0.0:21:28.32.0:21:29.41.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(439.408)}for your bag.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:30.62.0:21:31.61.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(90.405)}Seems like a waste.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:32.99.0:21:33.96.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(275.405)}Ladies love it.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:37.86.0:21:39.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(109.372)}Why are you telling me
Dialogue: 0.0:21:37.86.0:21:39.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(110.407)}all this. Stan?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:40.63.0:21:43.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(204.371)}'Cause. Gene.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:40.63.0:21:43.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(203.408)}you're selling fake for fake.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:43.83.0:21:44.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(201.405)}So?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:45.00.0:21:47.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(167.371)}Convince women these are real.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:45.00.0:21:47.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(166.408)}you get 10 times the money.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:01.52.0:22:04.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(125.371)}All this time.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:01.52.0:22:04.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(127.408)}I thought I hired a badass.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:08.06.0:22:10.75.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(135.372)}Lucky for me.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:08.06.0:22:10.75.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(136.408)}I got a prissy fashionista.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:12.49.0:22:13.46.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(439.408)}(CHUCKLES)
Dialogue: 0.0:22:19.40.0:22:21.06.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(227.408)}I really need to pass.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:24.00.0:22:25.60.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(120.408)}It's not just for me.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:25.71.0:22:27.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(108.408)}It's for my son.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:28.11.0:22:30.60.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(93.371)}Look. I know this
Dialogue: 0.0:22:28.11.0:22:30.60.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(93.408)}might not seem like
Dialogue: 0.0:22:30.71.0:22:34.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(126.372)}the most important thing
Dialogue: 0.0:22:30.71.0:22:34.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(128.407)}in the world to someone else.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:34.45.0:22:39.05.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(99.372)}but I literally
Dialogue: 0.0:22:34.45.0:22:39.05.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(98.405)}cannot move on
Dialogue: 0.0:22:39.39.0:22:40.98.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(129.372)}with my life
Dialogue: 0.0:22:39.39.0:22:40.98.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(129.405)}without it so...
Dialogue: 0.0:22:43.52.0:22:45.99.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(128.408)}If there is anything else
Dialogue: 0.0:22:48.06.0:22:49.46.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(156.405)}that I can do.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:53.73.0:22:54.76.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(183.408)}There's one thing you can do.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:55.90.0:22:56.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(171.405)}Name it.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:57.77.0:22:58.74.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(324.408)}Take your seat.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:00.47.0:23:01.44.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(211.405)}That's...
Dialogue: 0.0:23:18.96.0:23:19.93.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(107.408)}How many times?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:20.76.0:23:23.06.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(317.408)}(SPEAKING JAPANESE)
Dialogue: 0.0:23:23.60.0:23:24.90.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(227.407)}Yeah. same here.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:26.43.0:23:28.40.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(93.369)}TEACHER: You have seven hours
Dialogue: 0.0:23:26.43.0:23:28.40.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(93.408)}to complete the test.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:28.94.0:23:31.37.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(124.369)}First section has
Dialogue: 0.0:23:28.94.0:23:31.37.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(123.405)}a limit of 75 minutes.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:31.77.0:23:33.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(152.372)}I'll notify you when there's
Dialogue: 0.0:23:31.77.0:23:33.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(149.408)}five minutes remaining.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:34.44.0:23:36.57.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(103.336)}When the time is up.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:34.44.0:23:36.57.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(105.372)}please place
Dialogue: 0.0:23:34.44.0:23:36.57.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(103.408)}your pencils down.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:37.04.0:23:38.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(195.408)}Are there any questions?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:48.92.0:23:50.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(223.408)}BETH: Get 'em curry.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:50.49.0:23:51.52.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(324.408)}Curry?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:52.16.0:23:54.92.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(105.307)}Yeah. Jane's
